name: The Aussie Burger
description: A true classic with beetroot, a fried egg, pineapple, bacon, cheese, lettuce, and tomato.

name: The Aussie Pizza
description: Tomato base topped with ham, bacon, onions, and a cracked egg in the center.

name: Chicken Parma
description: Classic crumbed chicken breast topped with napoli, ham, and cheese. Served with chips & salad.

name: Fish Tacos (Baja Style)
description: Three tortillas with battered fish, cabbage, and creamy sauce.

name: Chicken Salt Fries
description: Hot chips generously dusted with legendary Australian chicken salt.

name: Thai Beef Salad
description: Marinated beef strips, vermicelli noodles, coriander, mint, and chili lime dressing.

name: Beef Cheek Ragu
description: Slow-cooked tender beef cheek tossed with pappardelle pasta and parmesan.

name: Pavlova
description: Traditional Aussie meringue topped with cream, passionfruit, and berries.
